Package: checkstring
Title: Common String Format Validation
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Maximilian", "Mücke", , "muecke.maximilian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-9432-9795"))
Description: Validates common string formats such as email addresses, UUIDs, URLs, IP addresses, and financial identifiers like ISIN, CUSIP, and IBAN, including check digit verification.
